kylin-video (2.1.0-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Solve the problem of video switching when deleting non playing files in playlist(Closes: #3576).
  * Support to set the volume when clicking the volume slider.
  * Update toolbar's icon.
  * Keep the window state when the window is restored from minimized.
  * Adapt to 4K screen.
  * Fix bug of video pause after minimization.
  * Automatic hiding of titlebar and toolbar in fullscreen.
  * Fix the bug that the titlebar does not hide when the video has finished in full screen mode.
  * Fix that Must construct a QApplication first.

